        List<StreamClient> list(Long roomId)
        Get all ClientList Objects of that room and domain This Function is needed cause it is invoked internally AFTER the current user has been already removed from the ClientList to see if the Room is empty again and the PollList can be removed
        Parameters:
        roomId - - id of the room
        Returns:
        - list of all clients in the room
